      <h1 itemprop="headline">{pageTitle}</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">The moments that define careers and lives are almost always moments of pressure — a negotiation, a crisis, a fork in the road that demands a response now. Yet pressure is precisely when the brain's decision-making machinery works worst. Here's how to fix that.</p>
      <div class="author-info">
